he stock's OWN history \u2014 never a buy call."},"data_quality":{"price_asof":"2026-06-17","fundamentals_fetched":"2026-06-19","has_fundamentals":true,"has_shareholding":true,"liquidity_warning":null,"note":"Market data is daily and current; fundamentals & shareholding are as of the last cached Screener fetch (quarterly/annual). Confidence is lower for thin or short-history names."}}